race.description: Gallagher Insurance Brokers Country Boosted Handicap
race.comment: MOONLIGHT DREAM (2) is knocking on the door and looks set to peak after missing by the barest of margins to SIR LUNCHALOTS here last start. Meets the winner 1.5kgs better this time and should blend into it perfectly from her gate. Expecting her to take plenty of stopping. SERENADING (4) has been freshened with 48 days after a disappointing effort here time when favourite. Folded too easy off a genuine temp, suspect that run was too bad to be true. Steps to 1400m and positive move with Boudvillain back in the saddle. Expecting sharp improvement.WONDERFUL MISTAKE (5) has returned in strong order this prep, this looks the testing material now. Likely to settle back from her wide gate and be saved for the final shot at them. SIR LUNCHALOTS (7) was a brave on speed winner last time and has more to offer third-up, though does meet MOONLIGHT DREAM worse at the weights. Still worth plenty of thought. COSSACK WARRIOR (1) is proving costly but deserves respect.
